#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rastertools.rst:16
msgid ""
"Aligns raster by resampling it to the same cell size and reprojecting to the"
" same CRS as a reference raster."
msgstr ""
"Poravnava raster preuzorkovanjem na istu veličinu ćelije i reprojektovanjem "
"u isti CRS kao referentni raster."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rastertools.rst:19
msgid ""
"**This algorithm is ONLY available in the** :ref:`Model Designer "
"<processing.modeler>` context. For other contexts, use instead "
":ref:`qgisalignrasters`."
msgstr ""
"**Ovaj algoritam je dostupan SAMO u** kontekstu :ref:`Dizajnera modela "
"<processing.modeler>`. Za druge kontekste koristite :ref:`qgisalignrasters`."

